<img src="https://biz-file.com/c/1909/516531-625x417.jpg" alt="Primedia Broadcasting scoops best Radio Media Owner Award at 2019 MOST Awards" width="625" height="417">The awards serve as an annual measure of the service efficacy of providers in the South African Media Industry. “The overall goal of the MOST Awards is to motivate media owners and media agencies to improve the efficacy of their businesses through service performance. To receive this acknowledgement two years in a row is testament to how we have worked extensively to hone our service delivery skills with our sales teams and engage our clients through a renewed and innovative trade marketing strategy”, said Eric D’Oliveira, Chief Executive Officer for Primedia BroadcastingD’Oliveira adds: “Paramount to revitalizing our approach from a sales and trade marketing perspective has been to deliver exceptional sales service, working with clients on unique ideation and showcasing a superior knowledge of our brands, the landscape and solving the needs of our clients. We strive to get better every day and are honoured to receive the acknowledgement from industry tastemakers.  For the latest news and information from Primedia Broadcasting visit: www.primediabroadcasting.co.za.